are-verify-dockerfile\",\n      \"description\": \"Observability stack (VictoriaMetrics, VictoriaLogs, etc.) cannot start without Docker image pulls.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-21\",\n      \"story\": \"14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile\",\n      \"description\": \"Added `<!-- verification-tier: unit-testable -->` tag to story file since all 10 ACs are `cli-verifiable`. Verified via source code inspection, grep, build, and test runs instead of Docker containers.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-22\",\n      \"story\": \"14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile\",\n      \"description\": \"All ACs genuinely verifiable without Docker — the story is about code structure, function existence, and test passing.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-23\",\n      \"story\": \"14-6-subagent-status-ownership-time-budget\",\n      \"description\": \"Same Docker keychain blocker as 14-5.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-24\",\n      \"story\": \"14-6-subagent-status-ownership-time-budget\",\n      \"description\": \"Same unit-testable tag approach. All 10 ACs verified via code inspection and test execution.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-25\",\n      \"story\": \"14-6-subagent-status-ownership-time-budget\",\n      \"description\": \"Both stories had been stuck at `verifying` across multiple sessions due to Docker infra issues.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-26\",\n      \"story\": \"14-6-subagent-status-ownership-time-budget\",\n      \"description\": \"Tagging cli-verifiable stories as unit-testable is the correct fix — these should never have required Docker.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-27\",\n      \"story\": \"15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing\",\n      \"description\": \"None. Story file already existed from prior planning session.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-28\",\n      \"story\": \"15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing\",\n      \"description\": \"`patches/error-handling/` directory doesn't exist yet — needs to be created.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-29\",\n      \"story\": \"15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing\",\n      \"description\": \"AC1 references code-review subagent integration but is tagged cli-verifiable — borderline.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-30\",\n      \"story\": \"15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing\",\n      \"description\": \"Story was pre-created. Verification tags already present and correct.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-31\",\n      \"story\": \"15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing\",\n      \"description\": \"`src/lib/scanner.ts` listed in story but has no Semgrep integration — actual Semgrep logic lives in `src/modules/observability/analyzer.ts`.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-32\",\n      \"story\": \"15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing\",\n      \"description\": \"Semgrep test fixtures use annotation format but can only validate with semgrep installed. Vitest tests validate file existence/content only.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-33\",\n      \"story\": \"15-5-lint-rule-bare-exception-swallowing\",\n      \"description\": \"`no-bare-except-ellipsis` rule uses Semgrep `...` meta