{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JyptpMQ9rrVqF56UUxGGJv","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-28\n     2→\n     3→### Session 58 — state corruption fix #42, no-op (2026-03-28T05:42Z)\n     4→\n     5→- **State corruption fix #42**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`, done count dropped from 74 to 70.\n     6→- Evidence: all 4 stories have proof documents in `verification/` and \"verified and done\" git commits.\n     7→- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done`, updated sprint totals (70->74), set epic-16 to `done`.\n     8→- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph stale in-memory state overwrites. 42nd occurrence.\n     9→- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n    10→- **CRITICAL**: Ralph must be stopped. 42 consecutive no-op sessions wasting tokens on the same fix.\n    11→\n    12→## Token Report\n    13→- Total tool calls: ~12\n    14→- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 5, Edit: 5, Glob: 1, Write: 1\n    15→- Files read: 3 unique, 5 total reads\n    16→- Redundant operations: None — known recurring issue efficiently fixed\n    17→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_013ditdZHLMnij4xDdHKwm53","session_id":"bb902526-e4a3-437a-baf7-59f73f360d2b","uuid":"41157bdc-f979-4fb6-8e51-7f5a48a8d0df","timestamp":"2026-03-28T05:43:32.320Z"}
